I don't know what make of gauges you are using, but VDO produces a flexible 
gauge mount that has 1, 2, or 3 holes, and it mounts under your dash -- that 
way you don't have to hack holes in your dash....  I've seen them on the Bus 
Boys website: www.busboys.com.

